'''''Kalif''''' was a [[Xiytiar-class heavy transport|''Xiytiar''-class heavy transport]] belonging to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperials]]. ''Kalif'' was part of the [[Imperial II-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial II''-class Star Destroyer]] [[Corrupter (Imperial-class)|''Corrupter'']]<nowiki>'</nowiki>s [[Corrupter repair convoy|vital resupply convoy]] lead by the [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|Nebulon-B Frigate]] [[Monitor (EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate)|''Monitor'']] to the ''Corrupter'' in the [[Mev system/Legends|Mev system]]. ''Kalif''{{'s}} cargo was "probe droids". The ship was then attacked by [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] raiders and was destroyed.

